{"tid":228801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警精英部隊下周反恐大演習 模擬應對恐襲保回歸盛事","createTime":"2017-05-04T07:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T08:46:06.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"788e588c15faf8745e7c3225f6c18ebb0d8a0941","tid":228801,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"全球瀰漫恐襲陰霾，今年七一香港回歸20周年盛事，料必有國家領導人訪港，警方連月密鑼緊鼓進行連串反恐演習。據悉，警方將於下周再度進行一連4天的大型反恐演習，除了有模擬跟蹤行動，其中壓軸演練在九龍灣輔警總部舉行，模擬有恐怖分子放置炸彈及挾持人質，將會出動拆彈專家、飛虎隊、反恐特勤隊、機動部隊、衝鋒隊等精英部隊，多達數百名警務人員參與，添反恐實力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/03/20170329_PO_%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9_%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F03%2F20170329_PO_%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9_%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8_02.jpg&h=dd89649b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方反恐特勤隊</span><br />\n<br />\n香港回歸20周年，國家領導人七．一前後勢訪港，警方將採最高規格反恐保安布防。而最新反恐演習將於下周一至四，在各區進行。據了解，演習首3天主要針對警隊應對恐怖襲擊事故的內部運作、指令收發和溝通演練，牽涉不同訓練單位、警區軍裝人員及交通部人員等。據悉，當中更會進行模擬跟縱行動項目，進一步加強搜集情報能力。<br />\n <br />\n重頭戲則是下周四下午至傍晚舉行的反恐演練，在九龍灣輔警總部舉行，據悉將模擬有恐襲事故發生，有恐怖分子在輔警總部建築物內放置炸彈，並挾持人質。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/03/20170329_PO_%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9_%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F03%2F20170329_PO_%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9_%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8_01.jpg&h=53066378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方反恐特勤隊演習</span><br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方屆時將會出動爆炸品處理課、飛虎隊、反恐特勤隊、機動部隊、衝鋒隊等多個精銳部隊到場應對，更會安排拆彈專家進行模擬拆彈，預料共有數百名警務人員參與。此舉除了有助再加強警隊各單位遇重大事故時的迅速反應能力、合作默契，更可向外展示警隊反恐實力。多名警隊高層，包括處長盧偉聰和副處長（行動）劉業成等，屆時亦會到場監督。<br />\n <br />\n此外，警方行動部警司蔡棟材指，若七．一有政要來港，警方會根據一系列因素作專業風險評估，包括國際及地區最新形勢、本港收到的恐襲情報、訪港人物的身分、其出席的活動，以及過往相關經驗等，全力部署保安工作。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/05/20151110_CR_%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E%E9%9A%8A_%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F05%2F20151110_CR_%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2599%258E%25E9%259A%258A_%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592.jpg&h=4c6ca40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">飛虎隊演習</span><br />\n<br />\n印尼總統日前訪港，警隊採較高規格反恐怖防，蔡稱每個保安行動有其獨特性，警隊已就回歸20周年活動設立督導委員會，將根據回歸15周年和類似活動的相關經驗作策劃。對於會否再次出動被指涉干擾民航處訊號的防爆專車，他只說如有需要會與相關部門溝通。蔡補充，警隊有概定機制檢視增添裝備的需要。<br />\n <br />\n由於鐵路、機場等重要基礎設施有較大可能成為恐襲目標，警方重要基礎設施保安協調中心專責與相關機構協調。蔡指出，警方一直與港鐵、機管局等保持緊密聯繫，不時進行演習，協調相關應變措施。他重申警隊是一支訓練有素及裝備完善的隊伍，並已制定應變措施處理大型事故。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2015/12/20110820_CR_%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%A4%E9%9A%8A_%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2015%2F12%2F20110820_CR_%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%25A4%25E9%259A%258A_%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592.jpg&h=6f61950b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方演習</span><br />\n<br />\n行動部警司梁詠霜表示，本港雖存在恐襲風險，警方暫無接獲任何具體情報顯示本港將面對恐怖襲擊，本港整體恐怖活動威脅級別維持「中等」，警方會時刻保持高度警覺和作好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/3-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%8B/2014108-%E8%AD%A6%E7%B2%BE%E8%8B%B1%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E4%BF%9D%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E7%9B%9B?r=w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F3-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BA%258B%2F2014108-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25BC%2594%25E7%25BF%2592-%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2581%2590%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E7%259B%259B%3Fr%3Dw&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=fbdc26a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/3-%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%8B/2014108-%E8%AD%A6%E7%B2%BE%E8%8B%B1%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E5%A4%A7%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-%E6%A8%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E6%81%90%E8%A5%B2%E4%BF%9D%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E7%9B%9B?r=w</a>"},{"pid":"81a72768cd09a88ba53ce7b9d93c6424c64b3095","tid":228801,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"示威者都應付唔到，點應付恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=81614293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so%2Fsource.gif&h=c6e30b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif&h=f7613e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26FPnpatcd94T0JLW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26FPnpatcd94T0JLW%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b585f810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/5KEXNDz3wuac/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F5KEXNDz3wuac%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3743800e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/7aPsXPUuzFrJ6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-sr