"2c75d7a3147fa4890787a66ecf473671a92980da","tid":228801,"uid":52910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"香港警察最失敗就係所有突發事故演習都係好早就預知<br />\n一早準備好曬 演習有咩用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該事前只可以部分人員知道<br />\n然後當日先分發非實彈彈夾比演習人員<br />\n只係比佢地知道係演習 但唔知其他詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca51307cea57b609d7effd3efd6a8382d359b34","tid":228801,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢啲演習可以練到啲咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n部門協調, 議器操作, 流程運作.<br />\n所有演習都同走火警差唔多, 都係簡單化令各人明白最簡單既運作.<br />\n<br />\n大鑊野從來都無得演習, 唔通真係整個三級火俾你走先叫先火警咩."},{"pid":"de34f940682f58df7c1baebd24d79afc9d80f357","tid":228801,"uid":53396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"自己預防自己演習呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea1ef0c15aca8acc1ff750c9dc1c90d131a0def","tid":228801,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港警察最失敗就係所有突發事故演習都係好早就預知<br />\n一早準備好曬 演習有咩用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該事前只可以部分人員知道<br />\n然後當日先分發非實彈彈夾比演習人員<br />\n只係比佢地知道係演習 但唔知其他詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔得啦，澳洲30年前試過特工處模擬喺市中心救/劫人質，之後酒店無人知報警，最後啲特工同維省警察喺鬧市駁火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b946188d46f7b4cf71e47cb2165ab1c96b0bf5a","tid":228801,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"習大大黎既話，到時實有好多大陸特工係附近啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係和平過平時"},{"pid":"5fb